title: The Lock and Key Library
creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of The Lock and Key Library, by Julian Hawthorne, editor.

A collection of classic mystery and detective stories, collected and edited by Julian Hawthorne.

Note: the second chapter of Dickens’ The Haunted House is not included in this edition.

(Summary by Julie VW)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: audiobook; librivox; short stories; mystery; detective; Julian Hawthorne.
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
